---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Sobre Apolonia — Nuestra Historia">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-red-dark to-brand-red py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="font-hand text-brand-gold-light text-lg mb-2 animate-fade-in-up flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 256 256" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M184,128a56,56,0,0,0-55.37-48H128A56,56,0,0,0,72,128v32a8,8,0,0,0,8,8h96a8,8,0,0,0,8-8Zm-16,24H88V128a40,40,0,0,1,80,0Z"/>
        </svg>
        Historia
      </p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
        Sobre Apolonia
      </h1>
      <p class="text-white/85 text-lg max-w-xl animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
        Desde 2020, seleccionando lo mejor para Playa Grande.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-[--radius-brand] p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-sm">
        <p class="font-hand text-brand-terracotta text-xl mb-4">Contanos...</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-red-dark mb-6">
          La historia de Apolonia
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-brand-charcoal leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Acá va a ir la historia del negocio. Cuando el cliente nos cuente 
            de dónde viene el nombre "Apolonia" y cómo nació el emprendimiento, 
            este espacio va a cobrar vida.
          </p>
          <p>
            Mientras tanto, lo que sabemos es que <strong>Apolonia</strong> 
            lleva <strong>6 años</strong> en Playa Grande, en Alem 3589,
            justo pasando el Sheraton. Un barrio que exige calidad, y Apolonia
            la entrega.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-brand-cream p-6 rounded-xl border border-brand-cream-dark">
            <p class="text-sm italic">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 256 256" fill="currentColor" class="inline-block align-middle text-brand-gold">
                <path d="M144,160H112a8,8,0,0,1,0-16h32a8,8,0,0,1,0,16Zm-8-48a8,8,0,0,0-8,8v16a8,8,0,0,0,16,0V120A8,8,0,0,0,136,112Zm40-64H80A40,40,0,0,0,40,88c0,21.32,13.66,40.19,34.58,57.12c11.46,9.26,18.52,21,21.38,33.58A24,24,0,0,0,119.48,200h17a24,24,0,0,0,23.56-21.3c2.86-12.55,9.92-24.32,21.38-33.58C202.34,128.19,216,109.32,216,88A40,40,0,0,0,176,48Zm13.16,91.72C174.07,155.91,164.81,173,161.13,192a8,8,0,0,1-7.85,6.44h-50.4A8,8,0,0,1,95,192c-3.68-19-13-36.09-28-52.28C52.27,128.74,56,107.22,56,88a24,24,0,0,1,24-24h96a24,24,0,0,1,24,24C200,107.22,203.73,128.74,189.16,139.72Z"/>
              </svg>
              <strong>Tip:</strong> Cuando hables con el dueño, preguntale:
              "¿Por qué Apolonia? ¿A quién homenajea?" Una buena historia 
              de nombre es el mejor branding que existe.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-brand-cream-dark">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-brand-red-dark text-center mb-12">
        Lo que nos mueve
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[--radius-brand] shadow-sm text-center">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 256 256" fill="currentColor" class="mx-auto mb-4 text-brand-fresh">
            <path d="M213.66,42.34a8,8,0,0,0-7.07-2.1C132.57,54.18,92.6,83.13,74.7,130.39c-5.29,14-7.87,28.48-8.86,42.27C52.13,153.75,48,131.14,48,112c0-64,80-80,80-80a8,8,0,0,0,0-16c0,0-96,16-96,96,0,51.79,26.62,79.74,47.34,92.69L56.73,207.6a8,8,0,0,0,11.54,11.06l23.34-24.34C103.21,201.1,113.21,208,128,208a8,8,0,0,0,0-16c-33.85,0-48-28.08-48-48,0-40,40-64,80-72-30.5,58.65-15.54,101.85-2.2,118.17a8,8,0,0,0,13.59-5.74c1.32-23.24,10.91-51.53,25.35-80.35C213.68,87.32,222,55.48,218.49,44.8Z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-brand-charcoal mb-3">Frescura real</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-brand-charcoal leading-relaxed">
            No es un eslogan: cada fruta y verdura viaja lo menos posible. 
            Si no está en su punto, no está en la góndola.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[--radius-brand] shadow-sm text-center">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 256 256" fill="currentColor" class="mx-auto mb-4 text-brand-terracotta">
            <path d="M232,136a8,8,0,0,1-8,8H200v24a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V144H168a8,8,0,0,1,0-16h16V104a8,8,0,0,1,16,0v24h24A8,8,0,0,1,232,136ZM88,96h80a8,8,0,0,0,8-8V56a32,32,0,0,0-64-8.19A32,32,0,0,0,80,56V88A8,8,0,0,0,88,96Zm16-40a16,16,0,0,1,32,0v24H96V56A16,16,0,0,1,104,40Zm-56,96H72v24a8,8,0,0,0,16,0V136h16a8,8,0,0,0,0-16H88V96a8,8,0,0,0-16,0v24H56a8,8,0,0,0-8,8A8,8,0,0,0,48,136Z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-brand-charcoal mb-3">Confianza de barrio</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-brand-charcoal leading-relaxed">
            No te vamos a vender cualquier cosa. Si hoy el tomate no está bueno, 
            te lo decimos. Preferimos esperar.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[--radius-brand] shadow-sm text-center">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 256 256" fill="currentColor" class="mx-auto mb-4 text-brand-red">
            <path d="M240,136h-8V120a8,8,0,0,0-2.34-5.66l-40-40A8,8,0,0,0,184,72H112a16,16,0,0,0-16,16v16H48a16,16,0,0,0-16,16v48H24a8,8,0,0,0,0,16H240a8,8,0,0,0,0-16ZM184,91.31,212.69,120H184ZM112,88h56v64H112ZM48,120H80v32H48Z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-brand-charcoal mb-3">Servicio sin fricción</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-brand-charcoal leading-relaxed">
            Pedido por WhatsApp, delivery sin cargo, cadete de confianza. 
            La propina queda a criterio, como siempre fue.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Location -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-[--radius-brand] p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-brand-red-dark mb-6">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 256 256" fill="currentColor" class="inline-block align-middle mb-0.5">
            <path d="M128,16a88.1,88.1,0,0,0-88,88c0,75.3,80,132.17,83.41,134.55a8,8,0,0,0,9.18,0C136,236.17,216,179.3,216,104A88.1,88.1,0,0,0,128,16Zm0,200.18C111.25,202.35,56,155,56,104a72,72,0,0,1,144,0C200,155,144.75,202.35,128,216.18ZM128,56a32,32,0,1,0,32,32A32,32,0,0,0,128,56Zm0,48a16,16,0,1,1,16-16A16,16,0,0,1,128,104Z"/>
          </svg>
          Encontranos
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-brand-charcoal">
          <p><strong>Alem 3589</strong>, Playa Grande</p>
          <p>Mar del Plata, Argentina</p>
          <p class="text-base">Pasando el Hotel Sheraton, sobre la mano izquierda.</p>
          <p class="text-base">Abierto de lunes a sábados, consultanos el horario por WhatsApp.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 h-48 rounded-xl bg-brand-cream-dark flex items-center justify-center text-brand-charcoal-soft text-sm">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 256 256" fill="currentColor" class="opacity-40 mb-2">
            <path d="M224,48h-.4L165.78,39.63a8,8,0,0,0-3.56.5L96.15,67.85,37.78,56.07A16,16,0,0,0,16,71.74V208a16,16,0,0,0,21.38,15.26L96,211.72l66.07,22a8,8,0,0,0,3.56-.5l64-24A16,16,0,0,0,240,194.26V64A16,16,0,0,0,224,48ZM96,199.72l-64-21.34V71.78l32,10.67V128a8,8,0,0,0,16,0V89.56L96,82.45Zm16-2.49L144,187.2V59.78L112,70.55Zm112-5.33-48,18V80.22l16-6V112a8,8,0,0,0,16,0V70.67l16-6Z"/>
          </svg>
          <p class="text-brand-charcoal-soft text-sm">Acá va un mapa embebido (Google Maps o similar)</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-brand-cream">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-brand-red-dark mb-4">
        ¿Querés conocernos?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base text-brand-charcoal mb-8">
        Pasate por el local o mandanos un WhatsApp. Te esperamos.
      </p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/5492235833114" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 bg-[#25D366] text-white font-medium rounded-[--radius-button] hover:bg-[#22c35e] transition-all">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/>
        </svg>
        Escribinos
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
